Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd love to hear Ichinokura-san's song.{idk anymore. bleh}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I feel like it'd help me get better.{fuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll sing because you said so, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.50,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan is late, huh?{on another note, WHY DOESN'T THIS GUY LEARN A NEW FUCKING SONG OH WELL AT LEAST THAT SAVES ME THE AGONY OF FIXING THE HORRIBLY TRANSLATED LYRICS OF AN ALL NEW MASTERPIECE}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,These are Mom's favorite flowers!{hm, rather than sepia, maybe I should add some kind of bloom or something}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,I'll take some to Mom in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Mom always smiles when she sees dandelions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,That's why, if I bring them to her, she'll get better again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:47.27,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Back then, I would gather flowers day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Mom! Mom! I brought you some more flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was nothing I could do.{probably could be better linked to the current situation}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Kyou, you brought me some dandelions again, didn't you?{DANDELIONS IN A VASE, YOU SEE FLOWERS IN THESE WEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEDS}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I promised, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Thank you.{k so would it be weird to make her mom's speech all bloom-y >__>}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Looking at the dandelions you've brought me always helps me forget about my sickness.{FUCK. FUCK. FUCK.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom's smile... She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Hey, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Why do you smile whenever you see dandelions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,You see, it's because the dandelions look so happy and carefree to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,They look happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,That's why they remind me of you, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Just like the dandelions, you always seem to be smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,That's why I smile whenever I see dandelions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Mom wasn't smiling because she was looking at the dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was smiling because she saw my smile.{"face" is a more accurate translation but I really like this phrasing better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I never smiled for Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:16:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:02.77,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.26,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, don’t try to take anybody else’s place.{lifted right out of episode 4, 17:54}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu.{I'm like 90% sure they just forgot to animate her mouth. I think that explains why it magically disappeared.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:14.49,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,You’re my older sister. Stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:19.08,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Okay, I will. I'll be right here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.60,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:27.44,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I... What the heck was I doing? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing that only I can do for Asu. The most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Onee-chan is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope she hasn't tired herself out worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to handle the hospital fees, too. Maybe I'm just being an annoyance to her.{for fuck's sake could these people be any more self-deprecating}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.16,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.09,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan's smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks just like a dandelion!{okay, I lost it. I just... }
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on being discharged, Asu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure to take it easy for a while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all you've done.{WHY DO YOU NEED TO THANK THEM, YOU'RE FUCKING PAYING THEM FOR IT :V}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Onee-chan, there's a place I'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't push yourself too much, okay?{tough it out like that anymore}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, at first, your cold was far worse than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so worried about you that I forgot to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right here, Mom asked me to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a long time ago, but this is where I heard it.{um wait...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,I'm your big sister! Do you understand me?{JESUS CHRIST HOW MANY TIMES WILL THEY REPEAT THIS}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with Mom's voice.{these are fragments. DO I LOOK LIKE I GIVE A FUCK}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,I ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,derp,Your big sister...{idk this is probably supposed to be broken english anyway but fuck that shitniggersidon'tgiveafucksofuckthatshityoufuckingfaggots}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Your big sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please protect her", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Asu, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't remember this{her} at all, but I get the feeling that that was what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I've promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will protect Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.61,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Mom, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.54,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,We're keeping our promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Onee-chan, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're in full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.98,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,We're very happy together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, this is bad! Really bad!
